import {
  Box,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemButton,
  ListItemIcon,
  ListItemText,
} from "@mui/material";
import Home from "@mui/icons-material/Home";
import React from "react";

const Sidebar = () => {
  return (
    <Box flex={1} p={2} sx={{ display: { xs: "none", sm: "block" } }}>
      Sidebar
      <List>
        <ListItem disablePadding>
          <ListItemButton compponent="a" href="#home">
            <ListItemIcon>
              <Home />
            </ListItemIcon>
            <ListItemText primary="Homepage" />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem disablePadding>
          <ListItemButton compponent="a" href="#profile">
            <ListItemIcon>
              <Profile />
            </ListItemIcon>
            <ListItemText primary="Homepage" />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem disablePadding>
          <ListItemButton compponent="a" href="#home">
            <ListItemIcon>
              <Home />
            </ListItemIcon>
            <ListItemText primary="Homepage" />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem disablePadding>
          <ListItemButton compponent="a" href="#home">
            <ListItemIcon>
              <Home />
            </ListItemIcon>
            <ListItemText primary="Homepage" />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem disablePadding>
          <ListItemButton compponent="a" href="#home">
            <ListItemIcon>
              <Home />
            </ListItemIcon>
            <ListItemText primary="Homepage" />
          </ListItemButton>
        </ListItem>
      </List>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Sidebar;
